{"tid":1806690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"已故阿仙奴名宿雷耶斯之子發亮！佩雷斯主席承諾包養到死年","createTime":"2020-01-01T12:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T13:18:51.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"15be45de898b67524d12322b675183efeb589bcb","tid":1806690,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/12/30/1/15941aabb403e11026e85d1a3b494289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F12%2F30%2F1%2F15941aabb403e11026e85d1a3b494289.jpg&h=d95e0102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小雷耶斯當選最佳球員+最佳射手<br />\n<br />\n　　在艾巴紮比舉行的Laliga希望之星比賽，皇馬小將荷西-雷耶斯（Jose Reyes Lopez）發亮，不僅幫助皇馬U12奪冠，他還當選賽事最佳射手以及最佳球員。值得一提的是，他是西班牙名將雷耶斯（Jose Reyes）的兒子。<br />\n<br />\n小雷耶斯出彩<br />\n<br />\n　　在決賽中，小雷耶斯攻入4球，幫助皇馬U12梯隊5-3逆轉擊敗西維爾，成功奪冠。整個系列賽，小雷耶斯在6場比賽攻入9球。<br />\n<br />\n悼念雷耶斯<br />\n<br />\n　　今年6月，前皇馬、西維爾球星雷耶斯因為車禍身亡之後，皇馬簽下了小雷耶斯，此外皇馬主席佩雷斯承諾將他包養到成年。"},{"pid":"408679184d01a4ed7f5b8a8be4fb67db17686e2a","tid":1806690,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"雷斯？"},{"pid":"b638f44b6a4b1826c9a3446d88bdf3fd0691c3e3","tid":1806690,"uid":35547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"肉酸"},{"pid":"3792a3d67a339ff0cb8f95e818cd62ade243b783","tid":1806690,"uid":20473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/12/30/1/15941aabb403e11026e85d1a3b494289.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\nU12?"},{"pid":"b75ce2011c1b118d584f3db1627622ea0db2b9b0","tid":1806690,"uid":16451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"佩雷斯主席真係正一死變態<br />\n12碎都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c23bdaa096f3186090e460ed22920